    <item>
      <title>高速感知幻觉：速度与灰度对机器人尺寸估计影响的基准研究</title>
      <link>https://xleave.github.io/posts/%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E5%B9%BB%E8%A7%89_%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8E%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E4%BC%B0%E8%AE%A1%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%87%86%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6</link>
      <guid>https://xleave.github.io/posts/%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E5%B9%BB%E8%A7%89_%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8E%E7%81%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E4%BC%B0%E8%AE%A1%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%87%86%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>本文定量研究了移动机器人在运动过程中速度与目标反射对比度（灰度）对红外传感器测量精度的交互耦合影响，利用 Pololu 3Pi+ 移动平台揭示了低对比度目标在高车速下的信号衰减和“感知崩溃”现象。</description>
    </item>
